Text: Howdy Zibbik. I am submitting this comment because I am searching for an "audio" recording of the friday july 11th performance of Queen at Wembley Stadium in 1986. I have the saturday july 12th performance. But I'd really like the friday performance which was the 1st of the two shows Queen did at Wembley in 1986. Would it be possible to post an audio torrent of this classic Queen concert? Much mahalos.
